花post裡面嘅相<br />\n<br />\n點解淨係整政府部門同公營機構呢？<br />\n因為佢哋發聲嘅震撼力比較大同埋小弟能力有限，未能夠整合晒各行各業嘅post<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲其實只係想post喺連登，而唔想擺喺facebook，歡迎pm我，我會即刻delete返<br />\n<br />\n而如果有喺政府部門或者公營機構工作嘅巴絲想post去facebook，歡迎喺facebook pm呢個page: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivilservantsflowers%2F&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=9e347bd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做"},{"pid":"e2ebdf459afaa0091853521cb158a88ff9d342f1","tid":1362894,"uid":236847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:46:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1a123650be401dac85db1a21a15854f9b49079","tid":1362894,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:03:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14b2229d37e10e1039db97c890873fc9b3ede1eb","tid":1362894,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:11:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">727 和理優 <br />\n不入村 不開波 <br />\n對家郁手會還拖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 727元朗 不反對3PM 自發11AM 水邊村 講咁多搞清楚時間先啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1363109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1363109</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/25/025139_1069cdf5884702ad86a217dcd2ddc4c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2F025139_1069cdf5884702ad86a217dcd2ddc4c7.png&h=c14c4c2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08b2ec7432ddf0e18f5664be893213007230e3c0","tid":1362894,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:18:23.000Z","msg":"終於最後一個良心紀律部